{"tid":1962464,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"【可能太似樣】南亞仔確診新冠病毒　父親被誤送入院","createTime":"2020-04-07T13:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-07T13:20:58.000Z","uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87339b5f0130769776f1b6f80efb369da036dce9","tid":1962464,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T13:14:32.000Z","msg":"一個尼泊爾家庭的兒子感染新型冠狀病毒，惟其父親昨（6日）被誤送入院。衛生防護中心今午（7日）在記者會交代事件。<br />\n<br />\n黃加慶稱，該尼泊爾家庭為早前確診者的密切接觸者，本已入住檢疫中心，新確診兒子是個案929，病毒檢測結果昨顯示為陽性，但「中間可能出問題」，其父親昨晚11時許被送入聯合醫院。他說，衛生防護中心在今午記者會前得知事件，已通知醫管局，安排該兒子入院；父親的病毒檢測結果陰性，會送回檢疫中心。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200407/s00001/1586250918141/%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E7%88%B6%E8%A6%AA%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E9%80%81%E5%85%A5%E9%99%A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200407%2Fs00001%2F1586250918141%2F%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E7%2588%25B6%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2599%25A2&d=BHyrWEjohbhGCquuSPOYYgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=3272263a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200407%2Fs00001%2F1586250918141%2F%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E7%2597%2585%25E6%25AF%2592-%25E7%2588%25B6%25E8%25A6%25AA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E9%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%2599%25A2&h=68f97885\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200407/s00001/1586250918141/%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E7%97%85%E6%AF%92-%E7%88%B6%E8%A6%AA%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E9%80%81%E5%85%A5%E9%99%A2</a>"},{"pid":"cab0e5a47734a14ac6ab4de9f7ffcce4398b055e","tid":1962464,